This is where you would provide all your actual domain knowledge and incorporate it into your

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:54.679
model as well as any of the existing seasonality and priors from your own data.

00:12:54.679 --> 00:13:00.799
We go and do this same thing for the non-transformed data as well.

